                <div class="ex-output">
<span class="output-status">// SSE</span>
GET /_realtime/stream?channel=chat.42
event: message.sent
id: 1713275400-000001
data: {"channel":"chat.42","event":"message.sent","payload":{"body":"Olá time","user":"Ana"}}

<span class="output-status">// WebSocket opcional</span>
php spark realtime:serve
→ autentica via token curto em POST /_realtime/auth
→ distribui o mesmo envelope para clientes conectados</div>
